latestIgtvVideos.title: Haldi..
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Butterflies in stomach, 
Teary swollen sleep deprived eyes, 
Dying with excitement at one moment, 
Wrecked with nerves at the other, 
Adrenaline high!! 

After you ride this rollercoaster of emotions, a sense of warmth and love is the only thing which can bring you calm and overwhelm you on your wedding morning. 

This haldi bash was that calm before the craziness of the D day. Surrounded by my loved ones..cheering me up!! 🎊♥️

•A tiny clip with the most cliche and a heart warming song•
